efore the race began, all 56 bikes were lined up in the transition zone except one.\", \"from\": 3277, \"to\": 3376, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 3299, \"to\": 3307}, {\"ngram\": \"all 56 bikes\", \"from\": 3315, \"to\": 3327}, {\"ngram\": \"the transition zone\", \"from\": 3345, \"to\": 3364}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yee breezed out last, found his spot at the far end of the bridge and began assembling his things.\", \"from\": 3377, \"to\": 3475, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Yee\", \"from\": 3377, \"to\": 3380}, {\"ngram\": \"his spot\", \"from\": 3405, \"to\": 3413}, {\"ngram\": \"the far end\", \"from\": 3417, \"to\": 3428}, {\"ngram\": \"the bridge\", \"from\": 3432, \"to\": 3442}, {\"ngram\": \"his things\", \"from\": 3464, \"to\": 3474}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He wiped each tyre clean with his fingers, then carefully positioned his bike in its stand.\", \"from\": 3476, \"to\": 3567, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"each tyre\", \"from\": 3485, \"to\": 3494}, {\"ngram\": \"his fingers\", \"from\": 3506, \"to\": 3517}, {\"ngram\": \"his bike\", \"from\": 3545, \"to\": 3553}, {\"ngram\": \"its stand\", \"from\": 3557, \"to\": 3566}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He laid down his trainers like they were made of glass, then stood, looked back and moved them ever so slightly.\", \"from\": 3568, \"to\": 3680, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his trainers\", \"from\": 3581, \"to\": 3593}, {\"ngram\": \"glass\", \"from\": 3617, \"to\": 3622}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then he strode back to the athletes' room inside the Grand Palais.\", \"from\": 3681, \"to\": 3747, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the athletes' room\", \"from\": 3704, \"to\": 3722}, {\"ngram\": \"the Grand Palais\", \"from\": 3730, \"to\": 3746}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He wrestled with \\\"imposter syndrome\\\" in his early career but in Paris, he carried the air of a man walking into his own living room.\", \"fro