o\": 4095}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He had focused on improving his swim over the past year and kept in touch with the early leaders in the water, emerging 18th, 27 seconds back, and hopefully without any stomach bugs ahead of the mixed relay.\", \"from\": 4187, \"to\": 4394, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his swim\", \"from\": 4215, \"to\": 4223}, {\"ngram\": \"the past year\", \"from\": 4229, \"to\": 4242}, {\"ngram\": \"touch\", \"from\": 4255, \"to\": 4260}, {\"ngram\": \"the early leaders\", \"from\": 4266, \"to\": 4283}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 4287, \"to\": 4296}, {\"ngram\": \"emerging 18th\", \"from\": 4298, \"to\": 4311}, {\"ngram\": \"hopefully without any stomach bugs\", \"from\": 4334, \"to\": 4368}, {\"ngram\": \"the mixed relay\", \"from\": 4378, \"to\": 4393}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You have got to have trust in the organisation that they are going to put you in safe conditions, and I am sure we will find out in due time if that's correct,\\\" he smiled.\", \"from\": 4395, \"to\": 4567, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"trust\", \"from\": 4417, \"to\": 4422}, {\"ngram\": \"the organisation\", \"from\": 4426, \"to\": 4442}, {\"ngram\": \"safe conditions\", \"from\": 4477, \"to\": 4492}, {\"ngram\": \"due time\", \"from\": 4528, \"to\": 4536}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His first change was quick, overtaking rivals through the transition area and exiting with a running jump onto his bike as he slipped bare feet into white cycling shoes.\", \"from\": 4569, \"to\": 4738, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His first change\", \"from\": 4569, \"to\": 4585}, {\"ngram\": \"rivals\", \"from\": 4608, \"to\": 4614}, {\"ngram\": \"the transition area\", \"from\": 4623, \"to\": 4642}, {\"ngram\": \"a running jump\", \"from\": 4660, \"to\": 4674}, {\"ngram\": \"his bike\", \"from\": 4680, \"to\": 4688}, {\"ngram\": \"bare feet\", \"from\": 4703, \"to\": 4712}, {\"ngram\": \"white cycling shoes\", \"from\": 4718, \"to\": 4737}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The roads had dried since the carnage of the women's race where wet patches had caused several hard falls, and Yee took turns at the front pulling the 13-strong lead bunch as Wilde chased.\", \"from\": 4740, \"to\": 4928, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4915, \"end\": 4920, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"score\": 0.9999999995757207, \"rank\": 3.0693081788212494e-10, \"text\": \"Wilde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The roads\", \"from\": 4740, \"to\": 4749}, {\"ngram\": \"the carnage\", \"from\": 4766, \"to\": 4777}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's race\", \"from\": 4781, \"to\": 4797}, {\"ngram\": \"wet patches\", \"from\": 4804, \"to\": 4815}, {\"ngram\": \"several hard falls\", \"from\": 4827, \"to\": 4845}, {\"ngram\": \"Yee\", \"from\": 4851, \"to\": 4854}, {\"ngram\": \"turns\", \"from\": 4860, \"to\": 4865}, {\"ngram\": \"the front\", \"from\": 4869, \"to\": 4878}, {\"ngram\": \"the 13-strong lead bunch\", \"from\": 4887, \"to\": 4911}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With three laps to go, Wilde joined the front in a group of 32 riders and they reached the transition zone together in a chaotic pack.\", \"from\": 4929, \"to\": 5063, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4952, \"end\": 4957, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"score\": 0.9999999995757207, \"rank\": 3.0693081788212494e-10, \"text\": \"Wilde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oscar_Wilde\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"three laps\", \"from\": 4934, \"to\": 4944}, {\"ngram\": \"the front\", \"from\": 4965, \"to\": 4974}, {\"ngram\": \"a group\", \"from\": 4978, \"to\": 4985}, {\"ngram\": \"32 riders\", \"from\": 4989, \"to\":